window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They were my bullies once.</b></p> <p><b>Three boys I hated more than anything.</b></p> <p>They made my life hell for a year - until I escaped their cruelty when my dad's job moved us away.</p> <p>I've never forgotten them though. Never forgotten what they did. And I know they haven't forgotten me.</p> <p>But when I'm offered a full-ride scholarship to the prestigious Clearwater University, I refuse to let old fears stop me from accepting.</p> <p>Because I'm not the girl I used to be.</p> <p>I'm stronger. Tougher.</p> <p>Angrier<i>.</i></p> <p>And if West, Reese, and Trent think they can fuck with me again...well.</p> <p>We'll just see who breaks first.</p> <p><b>This is book one of the Clearwater University series, a new adult reverse harem bully romance. It contains foul language and sexual situations.</b></p>"; 
